<h2>Tax Groups  </h2>
<p> Tax groups allow you to specify a tax rate, or multiple tax rates, for a specific type of product. Examples of a tax group might be Books, Electronics, Perishables, etc. </p>
<h3>Add a Tax Group</h3>
<p>To add a new Tax Group, enter the name of the group and click Add. After adding a Tax Group, click the name of the new Tax Group to <a href="AdminHelp.cfm?HelpFileName=TaxGroup.cfm">configure the group</a>.  </p>
